        {
            "id": 6403479,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 莫德納(MRNA-US)大漲5.02%，報50.65美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>莫德納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRNA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRNA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRNA-US</a>)截至台北時間01日02:31股價上漲2.42美元，報50.65美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量4,969,872（股），盤中最高價50.65美元、最低價47.96美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.27%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.58%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+3.43%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+5.32%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>莫德納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRNA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRNA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRNA-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-5.95%</li> <li>近 1 月：-9.97%</li> <li>近 3 月：+58.6%</li> <li>近 6 月：+86.72%</li> <li>今年以來：+63.55%</li></ul></section></main>",
